    <item>
      <title>大众汽车交付量因中国市场低迷和电动汽车市场困境而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/volkswagen-deliveries-fall-on-china-slump-and-ev-struggles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于电动汽车需求疲软以及主要中国市场的激烈竞争拖累了销售，大众汽车集团去年的汽车交付量有所下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/volkswagen-deliveries-fall-on-china-slump-and-ev-struggles</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利物价上涨，突破央行容忍区间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/hungarian-inflation-jumps-breaching-central-bank-tolerance-band</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利通胀率超出预期，超出央行的容忍区间，因为疲软的货币刺激了价格上涨并给货币政策带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/hungarian-inflation-jumps-breaching-central-bank-tolerance-band</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求疲软导致中国新增贷款 13 年来首次下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/china-s-new-loans-drop-for-first-time-in-13-years-on-weak-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，中国各银行新增贷款出现2011年以来的首次下降，凸显出在通货紧缩和房地产市场低迷的背景下，经济融资需求疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/china-s-new-loans-drop-for-first-time-in-13-years-on-weak-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 07:14:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
